<div class="section-title">Dentistry Marketing Consulting</div>

<div class="container">
        <div class="page-body">
                <h1>
  <li>Welcome</li>
</h1>
<p>The need for <strong>real</strong> change in how <strong><a href="/branding/marketing/" onclick="">dental marketing</a></strong> is done is <a href="#Dentistry-Care-Statistics">painfully obvious</a>. It is about time we did this the <strong>right</strong>&nbsp;<strong>way</strong>. Connect the dots to superior communication.
</p>
<br />
<div align="CENTER">
  <p><img src="/media/image/logo-connective-communication-pi-marketing-9.jpg" />
  </p>
</div><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: monospace; white-space: pre; "></span>
<hr /><strong><span class="Apple-style-span"></span></strong><strong><span class="Apple-style-span">&nbsp;</span></strong>
<p> <a id="Dentistry-Care-Statistics" name="Dentistry-Care-Statistics" title="Dentistry-Care-Statistics" class="anchor"> <strong>Dental Care, Dentists Visits Statistics </strong> </a>
</p>
<p>While dentists like you see the statistics in graphic detail, too many patients and consumers are missing the message. The evidence is <strong>overwhelming</strong>...
</p>
<ul>
  <li>&bull; 50% of the population is not accessing dental care on a regular basis </li>
  <li>&bull; 40% of that 50% is actually considered to be high income consumers!</li>
  <li>&bull; On average 22% of the population will lose ALL of their teeth by age 65</li>
  <li>&bull; No increase in dental visits over the last 14 years!</li>
</ul>
<p><em>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Other Site Resources: <a href="http://www.statemaster.com/graph/hea_ora_hea_los_of_nat_tee-health-oral-loss-natural-teeth">Tooth Loss Stats</a></em>
</p>
<p>The <strong>only</strong> way to make real strides is a connective approach...
</p>
<ul>
  <li>&bull; One-off marketing concepts too often merely tread water.</li>
  <li>&bull; Inflexible systems seriously limit your potential to provide consistently appropriate treatment.</li>
  <li>&bull; The lack of proactive, connective consistency greatly inhibits the enhancement of oral health appreciation.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong><em>Where to start? </em></strong>
</p>
<p><strong>&nbsp; Contact Niche Dental&nbsp;</strong>
</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>CALL</strong><span class="Apple-style-span">&nbsp;</span>Richard The Chwalek: <strong>866.453.1026</strong>
  <br /></li>
  <li>Fill out <strong><a href="/contact/">email form</a></strong>.&nbsp;</li>
</ul>
<p> <em>Sincerely, </em>
</p>
<p><em></em><strong>Richard Chwalek </strong>
  <br />
</p>
